OL,3,CThousands of pieces of rubbish left on
OL,4,CWales' biggest mountain
OL,6,FExpert climbers scaled the Trinity
OL,7,FWall gullies, a popular climbing face
OL,8,Fon the mountain, to clear litter while
OL,9,Fvolunteers also cleared the Miner's
OL,10,FPath.
OL,12,FSingle-use products accounted for 63%
OL,13,F(1,737) of the items retrieved. Of
OL,14,Fthese, the 809 drinks containers
OL,15,Frecovered were more common (29.3%)
OL,16,Fthan the 794 snack items found (28.7%).
OL,18,FThe BMC believes stopping the use of
OL,19,Fplastic drinks bottles is one of the
OL,20,F"simplest" ways of cleaning up the
OL,21,Fmountain.
