OL,6,FEnvironmental campaigners Trash Free
OL,7,FTrails said the presence of so many
OL,8,Fdrinks containers reinforces the need
OL,9,Ffor Deposit Return Scheme (DRS).
OL,11,FThese schemes are commonplace in
OL,12,FEuropean countries ` where they
OL,13,Foperate by requiring a deposit on
OL,14,Fplastic bottles and aluminium cans
OL,15,Fthat can be reclaimed either in stores
OL,16,For via "reverse vending machines".
