OL,6,FThe UK Government had planned to have
OL,7,Fa DRS in place by 2025 but this has
OL,8,Fnow been delayed until October 2027 to
OL,9,Fgive the industries involved more time
OL,10,Fto prepare.
OL,12,FThe charity Keep Britain Tidy
OL,13,Festimates the delay will mean 25
OL,14,Fbillion more bottles and cans being
OL,15,Flittered.
OL,17,FWestminster also wants to drop glass
OL,18,Ffrom the scheme as its inclusion would
OL,19,Fbe "problematic" for the drinks
OL,20,Findustry. Wales is the only Home
OL,21,FNation still opposing this proposal.
