OL,4,CWales' biggest mountain
OL,6,FAfter the clean-up, Tom Carrick, BMC
OL,7,Faccess and conservation officer for
OL,8,FWales, said: "The Yr Wyddfa Big Clean
OL,9,FUp was the first time we have accessed
OL,10,Fthe Clogwyn Y Garnedd gullies, one of
OL,11,Fthe rarest Alpine habitats in the
OL,12,FBritish Isles.
OL,14,F"One of the starkest issues was the
OL,15,Fvolume of single-use plastic bottles;
OL,16,Fthis appears to be one of the simplest
OL,17,Fitems to rid from the mountain.
