OL,4,CWales' biggest mountain
OL,6,F"A Deposit Return Scheme (DRS) in
OL,7,FWales and England, would encourage a
OL,8,Fmuch greater care and thought over
OL,9,Fwhat pollution was taken onto the
OL,10,Fmountain."
OL,12,FAlec Young of Eryri National Park
OL,13,Fsaid: "Microplastics have been found
OL,14,Fin every soil sample monitored on the
OL,15,Fmost popular paths up Yr Wyddfa.
OL,17,F"We see DRS playing a pivotal role in
OL,18,Freducing litter on the mountain, and
OL,19,Fpreventing harmful fragmented plastics
OL,20,Ffrom entering, and ruining, this
OL,21,Ffragile environment'".
