OL,4,CWales' biggest mountain
OL,6,FDom Ferris, Trash Free Trails' CEO,
OL,7,Fsaid: "Our research has shown that a
OL,8,Ffifth of interactions an animal has
OL,9,Fwith an item of single-use pollution
OL,10,Fwill end in death, and our volunteers
OL,11,Fare increasingly finding examples of
OL,12,Fthis occurring when an animal gets
OL,13,Ftrapped inside a bottle or can.
OL,15,F"We know from European case studies
OL,16,Fthat a DRS can eradicate a whole
OL,17,Fcategory of litter from our trails
OL,18,Fovernight; why are we allowing beloved
OL,19,Fhiking spots such as Snowdon to be the
OL,20,Falternative to a reverse vending
OL,21,Fmachine?"
